name: Sheringham Super King Velvet Headboard - Charcoal
description: Fit for a king, this headboard is joining our collection in luxurious charcoal velvet. Whether you're embracing the laid-back luxury of English country house style or the rich material mix of contemporary interiors, your bedroom will benefit from the addition of this freestanding headboard. The Sheringham can be rested between the wall and a king-size bed frame with no need for fixtures or tools; a simple and effective way to give your room a brand-new look.
